replies.bodyText:
Ok, I see where you're coming from, I initially did this to avoid the NullPointerException and have the more meaningful IllegalArgumentException with message instead.
I'm updating this to default to a negative value, to keep the best of both worlds.
private static final int DEFAULT_MINUTES_SPENT = -1;

[...]

int minutesSpent = exchange.getIn().getHeader(MINUTES_SPENT, DEFAULT_MINUTES_SPENT, int.class);
if (DEFAULT_MINUTES_SPENT == minutesSpent) {
     throw new IllegalArgumentException("Missing exchange input header named " + MINUTES_SPENT);
}

